------------------------
Introductory information
------------------------

Generated in neutral s2p1 configuration; semicore d shell included.

This Tl potential was generated recently by Jorge Iniguez.

--------------------
Intended environment
--------------------

Mostly for Tl in oxides where it is in the 1+ formal oxidation
state.

---------------------------------------
Summary of atomic transferability tests
---------------------------------------

There is a test for the s2 configuration in the distribution:

   nlm    all-elec      pseudo        diff

   520   -1.688778   -1.688695   -0.000083
   600   -1.226801   -1.226594   -0.000207

